query:
SELECT
            ti.id::text as "id!",
            ti.email as "target_email",
            ti.role as "to_role",
            ti.created_at as "timestamp!"
           FROM team_invitations ti
           JOIN teams t ON ti.team_id = t.id
           WHERE t.tenant_workspace_id = $1
           ORDER BY ti.created_at DESC
           LIMIT 5
